ptolemy.backtrack.eclipse.ast

Class ASTFormatter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
      • ptolemy.backtrack.eclipse.ast.ASTFormatter

  • public class ASTFormatter
extends org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
    An AST visitor that traverses an eclipse AST from a root node (usually a CompilationUnit object), and outputs the formatted Java source code. It is modified from org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.NaiveASTFlattener in Eclipse 3.0.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 5.1
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Thomas Feng
    See Also:
    ASTVisitor
    Pt.AcceptedRating:
    Red (tfeng)
    Pt.ProposedRating:
    Red (tfeng)
